## Mmm problem.  xterms require +/-4, other apps require +/-12
Mod4 KP_Multiply :Resize +8 0
Mod4 KP_Divide :Resize -8 0
Mod4 KP_Add :Resize 0 +8
Mod4 KP_Subtract :Resize 0 -8

